title: Instacart Reveals $428 Million in Profit but Slowing Growth Ahead of I.P.O.
description: Nearly a third of Instacart’s revenue came from advertising, and grocery orders were flat in the first half of this year, the company said.

title: Before Gran Turismo Inspired a Movie, It Drove Jann Mardenborough to Greatness
description: The PlayStation video game’s realistic cars and racetracks helped Jann Mardenborough find his calling as a professional driver.

title: Trump Returns to X, the Service Formerly Known as Twitter
description: Absent for more than two years, former President Donald J. Trump posted his mug shot on the site, now called X.
